<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-br">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Cadastro Realizado! - Central RPG</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Special+Elite&family=Oswald:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Oswald', sans-serif;
            background: linear-gradient(-45deg, #232526, #414345, #1a1a1a, #000000);
            background-size: 400% 400%;
            animation: gradientBG 25s ease infinite;
        }
        @keyframes gradientBG { 0% { background-position: 0% 50%; } 50% { background-position: 100% 50%; } 100% { background-position: 0% 50%; } }
        .font-typewriter { font-family: 'Special Elite', cursive; }
        .glass-card {
            background: rgba(10, 10, 10, 0.6);
            -webkit-backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="text-gray-200 flex items-center justify-center min-h-screen p-4">

<div class="glass-card w-full max-w-md p-8 rounded-lg shadow-2xl shadow-black/50 text-center">
    <header class="mb-6">
        <h1 class="font-typewriter text-3xl font-bold text-green-400" style="text-shadow: 0 0 10px #2f855a;">Cadastro Realizado com Sucesso!</h1>
    </header>

    <div class="text-gray-300 space-y-4">
        <p>A sua conta foi criada.</p>
        <p>Enviámos um <strong class="text-yellow-400">código de verificação</strong> para o seu e-mail. Por favor, verifique a sua caixa de entrada (e a pasta de spam) para ativar a sua conta.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-8">
        <a href="/verificar" class="w-full inline-block bg-yellow-600 hover:bg-yellow-700 text-black font-bold py-3 px-4 rounded-lg transition-colors duration-300 shadow-lg shadow-yellow-900/50">
            Verificar a Minha Conta Agora
        </a>
    </div>

    <div class="text-center mt-4">
        <a href="/login" class="text-sm text-gray-400 hover:text-white hover:underline">Ir para o Login</a>
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
